Onoja Uchenyo, whose stage name is Timikoda, is a young music artiste to watch out for. Timikoda took to music recently and is determined to make a name in the industry. His début and only official released song “Ego” branched out into the corners of Nigeria’s music industry same year he launched. The song featured another singer, Ojhey. Although the singer has one single to his name, he is yet to drop other songs he has penned. He said they would come out soon. The artiste has a perfect romance with afrobeat as well as other fusion of music genre. Timikoda’s song have a special sound effects that compel a music enthusiast to fall into memories of his notes. This is all thanks to his passion to make good music, which indeed he is achieving. The artiste, who pursues original songs only, expounded that he didn’t really need to see or hear anything to want to do music. He is neither ready to swerve nor veer towards any field other than the need to do music. While he chuckled about the fact that he is learning the ropes of music, Timikoda expresses gratitude to every experience music has brought his way. The graduate of architecture from Caritas University, is signed to Osho Records. 